  "name": "Nagaraja COU1 — Non-cannulated pedicle screw compression-bending credibility assessment (Minimal Profile)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for FEA prediction of ASTM F1717 static compression-bending performance of a non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw construct. The FEA model ensemble (FDA, Ansys, DePuy Synthes) is compared against N=11 experimental constructs across two laboratories. Intended use is pre-market submission support for a Class II spinal fixation device under 21 CFR 888.3076; the model is applied specifically to the compression-bending load case at the L4-L5 spinal level in an adult population. All 13 V&V 40 factors assessed; one factor (Test conditions) achieved level below required due to single test condition coverage.",
  "bindsRequirement": "https://uofa.net/nagaraja/req/f1717-compression-bending-performance",
  "bindsClaim": "https://uofa.net/nagaraja/claim/fea-predicts-f1717-compression-bending-within-10pct",
